  <description type="morphology">Stems 5–80 cm. Leaves: petiole ca. 2–15 mm or absent; blade 2–7(–8) × 0.5–2 cm, base cuneate, margin teeth acute or mucronulate. Perianths 2–4.5 mm diam. (including wing), ± tomentose, often becoming glabrous and reddish. Seeds 1.5 mm diam. 2n = 36.</description>
